      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Now, can you make it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Yes. Since I can't grab smoke, in order to make that into an armour, I needed a method to crystallize it. But, I never imagined I could crystallize it this easily with the help of holy water... Is this the power of purification?</html>]]></talk_question>
