      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Haha, almost perfect. However, this isn't the way to get a pure crystal. Only if there was a way to get the crystal from the monster at the Collapsed Mine... Oh! There may be a way...</html>]]></talk_question>
